Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:03.37,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}ぐるぐる廻せ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.61,0:03:06.48,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}この魔法の杖で
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:12.51,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}涙とSunny day 混ぜたら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:16.22,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}淋しがりやさん
