Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:15.58,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}那時候的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.97,0:02:19.32,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}對著無法起飛的螺旋槳做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.35,0:02:23.78,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}朝著天空的另一半抬頭望去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:26.89,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}光著腳丫肆意奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:31.33,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}我們永遠都是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.14,0:02:38.42,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}無論誤會與否 就是對生活充滿自信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:51.77,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}如同把重要的寶物 藏起來一樣
