Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.61,0:03:06.48,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}用這根魔法之杖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:12.51,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}把眼淚和晴天混合起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:16.22,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}怕寂寞的小孩
